# This directory holds statically-linked proot binaries
# bundled with the pyproot package.
#
# Naming convention:  proot-<arch>
#
#   proot-x86_64   — Linux x86-64
#   proot-aarch64  — Linux ARM64
#   proot-armv7l   — Linux ARMv7
#   proot-i386     — Linux x86-32
#
# Run scripts/download_binaries.py to populate this directory
# before building the wheel:
#
#   python scripts/download_binaries.py
#
# Or install the package without bundled binaries and let pyproot
# auto-download at first use (~/.cache/pyproot/).
